  "global_context": {
    "plan_summary": "Implement the plugin system specified in docs/PLUGINS.md (branch docs/plugin-system). Three levels: Plugin -> Module -> Instance, with capability QObjects (IAccount/IFeed/ISigner/IThemeProvider) exposed to other modules via implemented()-gated async request/signal methods. UI is pushed to a Host singleton. Static-Qt host re-exports Qt for runtime plugins. 27 phases, one reviewable commit each, in dependency order."
